flowchart TB
    subgraph LOOP["AGENT LOOP — Maria's Requirements Document"]
        CTX["📋 **CONTEXT**<br/>• Maria's prompt: Italian webshop, FR+BE, 2000 users, Hetzner<br/>• Odoo data: 150 orders/day, 1200 products, 45K€/month<br/>• Requirements template structure<br/>• Sub-agent results (functional + non-functional + cloud)<br/>• Memory: Maria's profile"]

